OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRogel Aguilera-Mederos:    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FColorado truck driver's    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsentence cut by 100 years  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A truck driver who was facing a        
OL,6, 110-year jail term for a deadly crash  
OL,7, has had his sentence reduced to 10     
OL,8, years, following widespread outcry.    
OL,10,FRogel Aguilera-Mederos' lorry crashed  
OL,11,Finto traffic in 2019, killing four     
OL,12,Fpeople in the US state of Colorado.    
OL,14,FAt trial he was convicted on 27 counts,
OL,15,Fand the judge said state law forced him
OL,16,Fto impose the lengthy sentence.        
OL,18,FBut on Thursday, Colorado Governor     
OL,19,FJared Polis commuted what he called an 
OL,20,F"unjust" sentence.                     
